{"tid":1096012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拒絕一國兩制」高雄遊行 揮掃帚喊「韓國瑜、掃國賊」","createTime":"2019-04-07T12:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T01:29:47.000Z","uid":35790,"like":84,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"143f3afc5aece938f246e78828ec5ed5cf6e8328","tid":1096012,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"「拒絕一國兩制」高雄遊行 揮掃帚喊「韓國瑜、掃國賊」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpOQ1u9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpOQ1u9N.jpg&h=331dd3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者方志賢／高雄報導〕「拒絕一國兩制，打造台灣新國家」高雄大遊行今下午吸引2、3000人走上街頭，遊行隊伍最後抵達高雄市政府，並在市府前撕毀巨幅《告台灣同胞書》40週年習近平談話，抗議民眾還揮動掃帚，高喊「韓國瑜、掃國賊」，以表達捍衛主權的立場。<br />\n<br />\n為抗議韓國瑜進入中聯辦，涉出賣台灣主權，由台灣各領域公民運動工作者組成的台灣公民陣線，今下午在高雄前鎮勞工公園舉辦「拒絕一國兩制，打造台灣新國家」大遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n約下午3點半，接力短講結束，隨即展開遊行，為擔心有不同立場民眾鬧場，高雄市警局出動上百名警力警戒，約下午近4時30分許，遊行隊伍抵達高雄市府。<br />\n<br />\n台灣公民陣線發起人賴中強隨即站上宣傳車，拿出巨幅《告台灣同胞書》40週年習近平談話，他強調這次遊行是為了抗議韓國瑜，並向中國清楚表達拒絕一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n賴中強批評韓國瑜走進中聯辦，以行動向中聯辦及中國北京政府磕頭，用行動為一國兩制背書，為抗議中國，賴中強帶領群眾一起撕毀手中「拒絕一國制」看板的及宣傳車上的巨幅《告台灣同胞書》40週年習近平談話。<br />\n<br />\n現場民眾也高呼「主權不能賣」、「民主不能賣」、「台灣中國一邊一國」、「拒絕一國兩制」、「今日香港、明日台灣」等口號。活動最後由民眾揮動掃帚，高喊「韓國瑜、掃國賊」以表達台灣人「拒絕一國兩制，打造台灣新國家」的強烈心聲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2751571_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-ltn-com-tw.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2751571_4.jpg&h=838381a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抗議民眾揮動掃帚，高喊「韓國瑜、掃國賊」。（記者方志賢攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2751571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2751571&d=Qy2hiQzhAVWh7XuXj3aMUQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=73a6b239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/m.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2751571</a>"},{"pid":"045020f580953d78de2db1111901a0bcfa6314c3","tid":1096012,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3565e3b766e54fafe82500f040582a6568ddcdf","tid":1096012,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636b82029d07241e2745631d15ae6f7d2ffbe386","tid":1096012,"uid":242630,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec82c34b48e7db254ce0a2443d83bc18986fd3e","tid":1096012,"uid":35430,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"入一入中聯辦就已經引到3000人遊行<br />\n其實連登係咪睇少左台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似港柒豬d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f81debb47fc8f3841321b19746810dd31fcb6e","tid":1096012,"uid":179409,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"好用唔用用「打造」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣真係俾支國污染得好緊要"},{"pid":"468b09488ad8cc5c5066f3034650879db1e82939","tid":1096012,"uid":52946,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9ec82c34b48e7db254ce0a2443d83bc18986fd3e","tid":1096012,"uid":35430,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"入一入中聯辦就已經引到3000人遊行<br />\n其實連登係咪睇少左台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/